_sText:
This map is completely original (to my knowledge). It is made with all the same textures as found in cs_office. The Two teams start on opposite sides of the map.. and generally meet in hallways.
There is no real advantage for either team.
12 players per team max.

This is my first ever map created after playing around in Hammer editor so some comments would be good.. preferably nice ones. Haha.

File size - 484kb (includes .NAV file)
